data.description: PRICE REDUCED!! Pride of Ownership shows in this Sprawling Ranch Home. Offering 3 Bedrooms, and 2 baths on an oversized lot.  Plenty of room to entertain with this open concept floor plan.  Recently remodeled kitchen with Granite Countertops and Stainless Steel Appliances.  Unfinished basement ready for you to finish to your liking. This home is tucked back in the neighborhood, is close to the Icehouse walking/biking trail and offers Lake Rights to Silver Lake thru the voluntary association. Extra Deep 2 Car Heated Garage (28x20 and 7 ft Door). Covered front porch and the backyard is fenced and has a covered patio, shed and dog run. Riverview/Wilmot School Districts. Still time to get in before the New Year!!
